<li><span><strong>Italiano</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_it.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Lietuvos</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_lt.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Português</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_pt.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Português (Brasil)</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_pt-br.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Русский язык</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_ru.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Српска</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_srb_cyr.pdf">PDF (цириллиц),</a> <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_srb_lat.pdf">PDF (Латин)</a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Polski</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_pl.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Slovenščina</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_sl.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>中文</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_cn.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><strong>日本語</strong>: <a href="https://d1ulmmr4d4i8j4.cloudfront.net/static/images/manifesto/ifixit_self-repair_manifesto_jp.pdf">PDF </a></span></li>
<li><span><em>Ajude-nos a concluir mais um!</em></span></li>
</ul>
<h2><span>Traduza o manifesto</span></h2>
<p><span>O mundo todo precisa ouvir essa mensagem. Se você quer ajudar, estamos compilando uma lista de <a href="https://pt.ifixit.com/Wiki/RepairManifestoTranslations"> textos sem formatação aqui</a>. Postaremos as traduções que recebermos aqui!</span></p>
<div align="center"><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/"><img src="https://i.creativecommons.org/l/by-nc-sa/3.0/88x31.png" alt="Creative Commons License"></a></div>
